Package com.flipkart.business

Interface SlotServiceInterface

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SlotService
    public interface SlotServiceInterface
    This interface defines the service operations related to Slot functionality. It includes methods for retrieving slots by gym center, getting a slot by ID, getting a list of all slots, adding slots for a gym center, and validating slots.
